<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></span></font><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Thank you for getting an insurance quote from Kingsbridge.&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>So far you have not opted to move forward with your quote. We understand that there can be many reasons why you may not want to continue with your purchase, so we want to check if these apply to you.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>Found cover elsewhere?</b><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you let us know the cover levels and the quoted price you have received or attach your quotation documents. I can give you a call to discuss if we are able to amend our original quote.<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br><b>Not currently working?</b><br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you are not currently working, we would discourage you from not holding an active policy; unless you’re stopping self-employment altogether, a break in cover could affect your business.&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>If you are&nbsp;<b>interested in proceeding with your purchase</b>, reply with the best time for me to call or give me a ring on&nbsp;<b>01242 808 740</b>&nbsp;and I’ll be happy to help.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white;">,</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>